I faced this issue with Firefox 73.0.1 on i3 wm.
Clicking rightmost pixel near the slider results in scrolling down in a big jump. The trough receives the click.

I worked it around by adding the following code into `~/.config/gtk-3.0/gtk.css`
```
scrollbar trough {
    border: none;
}
```

